{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-baidu-tongji","description":"添加百度统计到 Gatsby 站点","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","baidu","百度"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"sigoden","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e218d8c5674b6e72002b40adf65e6013"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/sigoden/gatsby-plugin-baidu-tongji"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-baidu-tongji\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-baidu-tongji\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-baidu-tongji</h1>\n<p>添加百度统计到 Gatsby 站点。</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-plugin-baidu-tongji</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"使用方法\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用方法</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ./gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-baidu-tongji`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 百度统计站点ID</span>\n      siteid<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"YOUR_BAIDU_TONGJI_SITE_ID\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// 配置统计脚本插入位置，默认值为 false, 表示插入到 body 中, 为 true 时插入脚本到 head 中</span>\n      head<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"获取-siteid\"><a href=\"#%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96-siteid\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>获取 siteid</h2>\n<p>浏览器进入 <a href=\"https://tongji.baidu.com/\">https://tongji.baidu.com/</a>, 依次点击: 管理（导航栏）-> 代码获取（侧边栏），进入如下页面</p>\n<p><img src=\"tongji-screenshot.png\" alt=\"百度统计界面\"></p>\n<p>上图代码中 hm.baidu.com/h.js%3F 后面的32个16进制数，就是该站点的站点id</p>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-baidu-tongji/","id":"f827565d-f03a-5de4-b444-116a3ba84efe"}}